#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.41:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.41:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga"
msgstr "4. Deities"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Dutiyavasasutta"
msgstr "41. Mastery of the Mind (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.41:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto cittaṃ vase vatteti, no "
"ca sāriputto cittassa vasena vattati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, having seven qualities Sāriputta has mastered his mind and is "
"not mastered by it."

msgctxt "an7.41:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.41:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto cittaṃ vase "
"vatteti, no ca sāriputto cittassa vasena vattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Having these seven qualities Sāriputta has mastered his mind and is not "
"mastered by it.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.41:1.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
